secondary_outcome.description:
for the surgical installation step: duration in minutes between the start of installation time (= end of anesthesia) and the time of first incision;
for the bone preparation step: duration in minutes between the time of the first incision and the hour of end of extraction of the femoral sections;
for the implant placement stage: duration in minutes between the start time of placement of the trial tibial implant and the time of the last stitch.
